      <h2 xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> <span class="mw-headline" id="Production">Production</span></h2>
      <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The film was originally offered to <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ken_Russell" title="Ken Russell">Ken Russell</a>, who chose instead to direct <i><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Valentino_(1977_film)" title="Valentino (1977 film)">Valentino</a></i>. Russell has described this decision as the biggest mistake of his career.</p>
